bug.short_desc: dleyna-server: Crashes due to double-free when destroying the same dls_upnp_t or dls_manager_t twice

long_desc.thetext:
Version-Release number of selected component: dleyna-server-0.5.0-2.fc23
Additional info: reporter: libreport-2.6.2 backtrace_rating: 4 cmdline: /usr/libexec/dleyna-server-service crash_function: g_type_check_instance_is_fundamentally_a executable: /usr/libexec/dleyna-server-service global_pid: 15015 kernel: 4.2.0-0.rc4.git4.1.fc24.x86_64 runlevel: N 5 type: CCpp uid: 1001
